    "description": {
      "value": "<p>You learn how to install a rudimentary shield that temporarily blocks damage. You gain the following new mod.</p><p><strong>Flickering Shield (armor):</strong> The item produces a temporary shield that protects its wearer from harm. The creature wearing the modded armor gains temporary Hit Points equal to 5 + your Intelligence modifier and regains Hit Points equal to your Intelligence modifier for every round the shield is active. The flickering shield lasts for 1 minute or until dismissed. The modded item or exocortex then becomes temporarily immune to your flickering shield mod for 10 minutes.</p>",
